00:05:32.148 --> 00:05:34.600
and was associated with mortality.

00:05:34.600 --> 00:05:36.630
So lower blood glucose
associated with mortality.

00:05:36.630 --> 00:05:37.463
Whereas in humans,

00:05:37.463 --> 00:05:40.250
higher resting blood glucose
was associated with mortality.

00:05:40.250 --> 00:05:41.120
And obviously,

00:05:41.120 --> 00:05:43.389
what we're mostly interested in is health

00:05:43.389 --> 00:05:46.200
and wellbeing of ourselves, of humans.

00:05:46.200 --> 00:05:48.690
I'm sure there are some people
