time restricted feeding,

00:12:21.947 --> 00:12:25.817
aka fasting, that involve
eating every other day,

00:12:25.817 --> 00:12:28.880
or eating one way for five days

00:12:28.880 --> 00:12:31.210
and then fasting for
two days, and so forth.

00:12:31.210 --> 00:12:34.396
So I'll be very precise about
what I mean and why I mean it.

00:12:34.396 --> 00:12:36.450
But for the time being,

00:12:36.450 --> 00:12:39.540
I'm going to refer to
time restricted feeding

00:12:39.540 --> 00:12:43.433
