00:19:54.380 --> 00:19:56.059
and what happens when you fast.

00:19:56.059 --> 00:19:58.596
I did an entire episode on eating

00:19:58.596 --> 00:20:01.620
and metabolism, and
hormones and other factors

00:20:01.620 --> 00:20:03.198
that impact appetite.

