you need to extend the fast
around sleep on both sides.

02:16:50.160 --> 02:16:52.332
You would place it smack dab
in the middle of the day.

02:16:52.332 --> 02:16:55.980
It would be a schedule in
which you started eating for

02:16:55.980 --> 02:17:00.412
instance at 10:00 AM. And you
