02:18:17.633 --> 02:18:19.197
If you exercise.

02:18:19.197 --> 02:18:22.451
For instance, I like to exercise
early in the day if I run,

02:18:22.451 --> 02:18:26.088
or if I do some moderate or
light intensity exercise,

02:18:26.088 --> 02:18:28.490
regardless of what type of exercise it is,

02:18:28.490 --> 02:18:31.976
I have no trouble waiting until
my feeding window kicks in

02:18:31.976 --> 02:18:33.957
around noon or even 2:00 PM.

02:18:33.957 --> 02:18:37.230
But if I do high intensity
weight training, for instance,

02:18:37.230 --> 02:18:38.063
early in the day,

02:18:38.063 --> 02:18:41.139
or if I run sprints and I do
