I kind of let it expand and
contract a bit around the eight

02:18:54.047 --> 02:18:57.100
hour mark, and feel perfectly
free to do that too.

02:18:57.100 --> 02:18:58.920
We're talking here in, in ideals,

02:18:58.920 --> 02:19:01.840
not in necessarily practicals,

