then it does seem that ingesting
protein early in the day is

02:19:17.471 --> 02:19:18.844
beneficial.

02:19:18.844 --> 02:19:23.155
That it can be more readily
converted into muscle tissue.

02:19:23.155 --> 02:19:26.520
And this has been demonstrated
