02:20:26.380 --> 02:20:29.810
Another thing that we can add
to this summary or key points

02:20:29.810 --> 02:20:33.660
related to time restricted
feeding is the use of glucose,

02:20:33.660 --> 02:20:36.045
disposal, agents, and or behaviors.

02:20:36.045 --> 02:20:40.500
If you find that you've eaten
too close to a period of time

02:20:40.500 --> 02:20:42.170
in which you would prefer to be fasting,

02:20:42.170 --> 02:20:46.242
that's when a 30 minute brisk
walk or even modest walk after

02:20:46.242 --> 02:20:49.039
eating can be beneficial,

02:20:49.039 --> 02:20:52.382
ingesting some lemon juice
or lime juice can help lower

02:20:52.382 --> 02:20:54.154
blood glucose somewhat.

02:20:54.154 --> 02:20:57.379
And then there are the things
like Metformin and berberine

02:20:57.379 --> 02:20:58.250
there,

02:20:58.250 --> 02:21:00.620
even some supplements out
there that combine things like

02:21:00.620 --> 02:21:01.764
berberine cinnamon,

02:21:01.764 --> 02:21:06.515
which can lower blood glucose
and things like chromium and

02:21:06.515 --> 02:21:09.160
things that have a mild
effect on blood glucose,

02:21:09.160 --> 02:21:14.160
but berberine and Metformin
are very high potency glucose

02:21:14.708 --> 02:21:16.092
disposal agents.

02:21:16.092 --> 02:21:18.740
And I mentioned earlier why you
would want to approach those

02:21:18.740 --> 02:21:21.187
with the appropriate level
of caution and figure out the

02:21:21.187 --> 02:21:23.470
dosages for you, and, and for some people,

02:21:23.470 --> 02:21:26.307
the dosages will be zero
milligrams is going to be ideal.

02:21:26.307 --> 02:21:29.810
And then of course we discussed
how making sure that you're

02:21:29.810 --> 02:21:32.682
ingesting enough fluids in
particular water and salt,

02:21:32.682 --> 02:21:36.756
especially if you're using
caffeine in order to increase

02:21:36.756 --> 02:21:38.120
your levels of alertness,

02:21:38.120 --> 02:21:40.530
regardless of where that caffeine
source comes from coffee,

02:21:40.530 --> 02:21:41.699
tea, or otherwise,

02:21:41.699 --> 02:21:45.090
that can cause the excretion
of sodium and can lead to a

02:21:45.090 --> 02:21:46.000
kind of shakiness,

02:21:46.000 --> 02:21:50.670
a lightheadedness and the
feelings of hunger that may or may

02:21:50.670 --> 02:21:52.968
not be related to blood glucose.

02:21:52.968 --> 02:21:55.030
Some people genuinely need to eat.

02:21:55.030 --> 02:21:56.830
I certainly would not
