where it's dangerous.

02:21:58.837 --> 02:22:02.091
Certainly if you are
diabetic, you, and in fact,

02:22:02.091 --> 02:22:03.180
for all people,

02:22:03.180 --> 02:22:07.450
you should consult with your
physician when exploring any

02:22:07.450 --> 02:22:09.706
major changes to diet or
additions or subtractions of

02:22:09.706 --> 02:22:11.088
anything, including supplementation,

02:22:11.088 --> 02:22:14.998
